                "actions": {
                    "value": "2"
                },
                "description": {
                    "value": "<div data-visibility=\"gm\">\n<p>The construct breathes in one of two ways, then can't use Breath Weapon again for [[/br 1d4 #rounds]]{1d4 rounds}.</p>\n</div><p>- Flame (arcane, evocation, fire) A blast of flame deals [[/r 15d10 # fire damage]]{15d10 fire damage} to all creatures in a 60-foot cone (<span data-pf2-saving-throw=\"reflex\" data-pf2-traits=\"damaging-effect,arcane, evocation, fire\" data-pf2-label=\"Breath Weapon DC\" data-pf2-dc=\"45\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">basic Reflex</span> save). This fire damage does not harm objects or constructs.</p>\n<p>- Weakening Gas (arcane, necromancy) A cloud of gold-flecked gas forces each creature in a 60-foot cone to attempt a <span data-pf2-saving-throw=\"fortitude\" data-pf2-traits=\"arcane, necromancy\" data-pf2-label=\"Breath Weapon DC\" data-pf2-dc=\"45\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">Fortitude</span> save; the effect lasts 1 minute.</p>\n<div data-visibility=\"gm\">\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Enfeebled]{Enfeebled 2}.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Enfeebled]{Enfeebled 5}.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The creature is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Enfeebled]{Enfeebled 8}.</p>\n</div>"
                },
